lead_paragraph: Gonzalo Higuain was a distant memory as Napoli produced a rousing display to beat last season's quarter-finalists Benfica 4-2 in the Champions League on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Higuain a Distant Memory as Napoli Thump Benfica
